show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/fmsLtg
show.description: A poor village girl, wronged and heartbroken, flees to the city for survival—only to cross paths with the man who once shattered her life. Now the owner of the hotel where she works, he appears as a charming partner to her own younger sister. A tangled story of betrayal, secrets, and fate’s cruel games unfolds—where past and present collide in unexpected ways.
